{"type": "article", "id": 30112, "title": "琴酒和朗姆酒包装", "description": "", "date": "2016-07-25T23:06:26Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 400262, "comment_count": 5, "praise_count": 75, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160725224849khAj15wIRN4OK8XP.jpg", "contents": "<p>          </p><p>初看到 Oruka 这两个一金一银的圆环时，你或许还以为是某种风格奇特的家饰。在约鲁巴语中 Oruka 意味着圆环，<a href=\"http://digitalfish.tv/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Digital Fish</a> 正是以此为灵感设计了这套琴酒和朗姆酒的概念包装，经过旋转才能顺利倒出酒来。除了大胆地舍弃传统的瓶装改用精致优雅的圆环容器之外，内侧还根据 shot 标上了刻度。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-active medium-insert-images-wide\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160725230306Si3dqkyVHBJPWhob.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.676000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"medium-insert-image-active\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"medium-insert-caption-placeholder\"></figcaption></figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160725230306QJ5gM8WzP4DEiC1h.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.592000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607252303066LRqJ29F3Sx8ucNt.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.676000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160725230307Rx1AgJn6XeupPI2S.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.900000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>"}